creator: Spare Labs Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The CitySquare Mobile Pantry app will allow you to see when your groceries are on their way and receive important messages.

Once your groceries are out for delivery, you will be able to track when your groceries will arrive at your doorstep and receive a text message once they have been dropped off. This app will also allow you to get messages on changes to the service, ways to provide feedback, and other important communications. Please note, use of this app is limited to individuals and families who have been accepted into the CitySquare Mobile Pantry Program.
